Server: Werkzeug/3.1.3 Python/3.10.12
Date: Sat, 02 May 2026 13:29:57 GMT
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Length: 22
Connection: close


The remote HTTPS server does not send the HTTP
&quot;Strict-Transport-Security&quot; header.
</plugin_output>
</ReportItem>
