  High Strength Ciphers (&gt;= 112-bit key)

    Name                          Code             KEX           Auth     Encryption             MAC
    ----------------------        ----------       ---           ----     ---------------------  ---
    TLS_AES_128_GCM_SHA256        0x13, 0x01       -             -        AES-GCM(128)           SHA256
    TLS_AES_256_GCM_SHA384        0x13, 0x02       -             -        AES-GCM(256)           SHA384
    TLS_CHACHA20_POLY1305_SHA256  0x13, 0x03       -             -        ChaCha20-Poly1305(256) SHA256


SSL Version : TLSv1.2
  High Strength Ciphers (&gt;= 112-bit key)

    Name                          Code             KEX           Auth     Encryption             MAC
    ----------------------        ----------       ---           ----     ---------------------  ---
    DHE-RSA-AES-256-CCM-AEAD      0xC0, 0x9F       DHE           RSA      AES-CCM(256)           SHA-384
    DHE-RSA-AES-256-CCM8-AEAD     0xC0, 0xA3       DHE           RSA      AES-CCM8(256)          SHA-384
    DHE-RSA-AES256-SHA384         0x00, 0x9F       DHE           RSA      AES-GCM(256)           SHA384
    ECDHE-RSA-AES256-SHA384       0xC0, 0x30       ECDHE         RSA      AES-GCM(256)           SHA384
    DHE-RSA-AES256-SHA            0x00, 0x39       DHE           RSA      AES-CBC(256)           SHA1
    DHE-RSA-AES256-SHA256         0x00, 0x6B       DHE           RSA      AES-CBC(256)           SHA256
    ECDHE-RSA-AES256-SHA          0xC0, 0x14       ECDHE         RSA      AES-CBC(256)           SHA1
    ECDHE-RSA-AES256-SHA384       0xC0, 0x28       ECDHE         RSA      AES-CBC(256)           SHA384

The fields above are :

  {Tenable ciphername}
  {Cipher ID code}
  Kex={key exchange}
  Auth={authentication}
  Encrypt={symmetric encryption method}
  MAC={message authentication code}
  {export flag}
</plugin_output>
